---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = "June 2026";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of service for Democratic AI Consulting."
>
  <section class="pt-44 pb-24 px-6 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-coral mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-[36px] font-bold tracking-tight text-ink mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-[14px] text-mute mb-12">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-[16px] text-mute leading-body">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Agreement to terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing or using <a href="https://demoaiconsulting.com" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">demoaiconsulting.com</a>, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree, do not use this website.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Use of this website</h2>
          <p>This website is provided for informational purposes. You may use it to learn about Democratic AI Consulting's services and to book consultations. You may not use it for any unlawful purpose or in any way that could harm the website or its users.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Consulting services</h2>
          <p>Specific terms for consulting engagements are set out in a separate engagement letter or service agreement between Democratic AI Consulting and each client. These website terms do not constitute a consulting agreement.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>All content on this website, including text, graphics, and brand assets, is the property of Democratic AI Consulting. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works without written permission.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Limitation of liability</h2>
          <p>Democratic AI Consulting provides this website "as is." We make no warranties regarding accuracy, completeness, or availability. To the fullest extent permitted by law, we disclaim all liability for any damages arising from use of this website.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Governing law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of New York, United States, without regard to conflict of law principles.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Changes</h2>
          <p>We may update these terms at any time. The date at the top of this page reflects the most recent update. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance.</p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-[20px] font-semibold text-ink mb-3">Contact</h2>
          <p>Democratic AI Consulting<br />Austin Quinn<br />New York, NY<br /><a href="mailto:austinquinn1999@gmail.com" class="text-brand-blue hover:underline">austinquinn1999@gmail.com</a></p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
